{
  "stem": "25773.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I had to pick each crab, and put in the bucket, and cover it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Next day, it was all plunged into boiling water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they made a big feast and ate, and ate, and cooked, and drank-- drank vodka.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My cousin was excellent at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Anyway, soon after this-- yes, very soon after that-- he brought his mother from the place in Zielonka, where she was hiding, into the apartment where we lived.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And it was quite dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because the concierge were downstairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The concierge, at any rate, you know, are very nosy people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But these particular Polish ones-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they decided-- and they-- and they-- sort of, they made illicit-- illicit drinks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Anyway, she was not allowed to walk, talk-- she was allowed to walk, but not to talk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So like, she would be an invisible living person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And she lived with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And after a few months, living like that-- very short time, one or two months-- one night, my cousin, the little girl, and-- the three of them disappeared.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We got up in the morning with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they were not there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Either they were frightened, or afraid, or didn't want to-- afterwards, we asked them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I met them after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They left us helpless like that-- me and my old aunt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Without even-- that was in the Zielonka.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I might mention that during the course of the few months, we met a family called [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kerschnerski. ?] We met the [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kerschnerski ?] family, and they were very charming people--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Zielonka-- who were some-- who were friends of the woman who was hiding my aunt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this family, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kerschnerski, ?] were not quite stupid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They realized that something is fishy here with me, and this, and that, and that.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
